  "time_ut": 1660664985,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0ba4\u0b95\u0bb5\u0bb2\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Information received by Sajith",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa has said that the government is taking steps to give the posts of chairpersons of the main committees in the Parliament to the opposition.",
        "He also said that the opposition party will provide cooperation for the good programs of the government without getting ministerial posts.",
        "Sajith Premadasa said the above while speaking to the media at the office of the Leader of the Opposition.",
        "We are completely opposed to increasing the burden on the people of the country by tasting the bones of ministerial posts, and we will hear the voices of the people of the country. We know what's on their minds. Therefore, we will take forward the programs for the well-being of the people of the country.",
        "We do not need ministerial positions to deal with the people of the country when the country is facing crisis conditions. It is known that the government is taking steps to give the positions of chairpersons of committees in the parliament especially to the opposition parties. He also said that the government should do it.",
        "The leader of the opposition party also said that the leadership positions of the departmental supervision committees should also be given to the opposition parties."
      ],
